HEADWORD: Actualization
<hw>Ac`tu*al*i*za"tion</hw></mhw>
<pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A making actual or really existent;
giving the appearance of reality.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>
<rj><au>Emerson.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> realization, realisation.</syn>⟦br⟧
